Working in pairs - 

1.      Create a new team repository (global/local).

2.      Create a new Java Project.

3.      Add the above product skeleton class to the project. Modify project/product skeleton to include a User Defined Exception Handler.

4.      Design Equivalence Partition/BVA tests for both methods. 100% EP and BVA coverage must be achieved.

5.      Create a corresponding Test Class.

6.      Write the corresponding JUnit tests.

7.      Run the JUnit tests so that they fail.

8.      Show your work to your tutor.

9.      Write Product Code.

10.    Run Tests until all tests pass.